<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Subscription Activated</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #2d7a3a; padding: 24px 32px; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .body { padding: 32px; color: #333; }
    .body p { line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .info-box { background: #f0f7f1; border-left: 4px solid #2d7a3a; padding: 16px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 16px 32px; background: #f4f4f4; color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>BeOrchid — Subscription Activated</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Your <strong>{{planName}}</strong> subscription is now active.</p>
      <div class="info-box">
        <p style="margin:0;">{{summary}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>Log in to the BeOrchid dashboard to start using your new features.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      You are receiving this email because email notifications are enabled in your BeOrchid settings.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
